Configuration
public class JettyWebXmlConfiguration
extends AbstractConfiguration

JettyWebConfiguration. Looks for Xmlconfiguration files in WEB-INF. Searches in order for the first of jettyX-web.xml, jetty-web.xml or web-jetty.xml
